ComicInfo.Title: August 2009 - November 2009
ComicInfo.Summary:
This issue: SuperMilo obliviously takes down a couple of electronics thieves and briefly reminisces about his origin story over a cup of coffee.
Series Description: When a lazy and self-centered tabby cat owned by a struggling cartoonist is suddenly given intelligence and super powers, Clemmons and Twin City gain a new protector – and nightmare! Will SuperMilo’s friends help him learn that being a hero is more than looking good for the camera, or will he destroy his beloved city in the process?
